  please.

  06 Feb 2004; Jeremy Huddleston <eradicator@gentoo.org>
  galan-0.3.0_beta3.ebuild, files/galan-0.3.0_beta3-gcc2_fix.patch:
  Added patch to fix gcc2 compile (Bug #40515). Added =dev-libs/fftw-2* to
  DEPEND (Bug #40514). Both fixes thanks to Tristan Henderson
  <T.Henderson@cs.ucl.ac.uk>.

*galan-0.3.0_beta3 (04 Feb 2004)

